AboutFilemanagerWhat = What is TinyFileManager?
AboutFilemanagerWhatDesc = TinyFileManager is a simple, fast and small web-based file manager in a single PHP file. It provides a web interface to browse, upload, edit, and manage files on your server with an intuitive interface.
AboutFilemanagerIntegration = Integration
AboutFilemanagerIntegratedBy = This module was integrated into Dolibarr by
AboutFilemanagerFeatures = Key Features
AboutFilemanagerFeature1 = Browse and manage files and directories on your server
AboutFilemanagerFeature2 = Upload, download, copy, move, and delete files
AboutFilemanagerFeature3 = Create and edit text files with syntax highlighting
AboutFilemanagerFeature4 = View images, PDFs, and other documents inline
AboutFilemanagerFeature5 = Create zip archives and extract compressed files
AboutFilemanagerFeature6 = Search files by name
